  "title": "Frontline Customer Service (Healthcare / Hospitals) - HMZT",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are hiring </strong><u><strong>Customer Service (Healthcare)</strong></u><strong> to be outsourced to reputable hospitals and medical\ninstitutions!</strong></p><p><strong>Many vacancies available!</strong></p><p><u><strong>Job Scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Answer patients’ enquiries and needs</li><li>Help with patient registration</li><li>Schedule appointments for patients</li><li>Handle phone calls</li><li>Other ad-hoc admin duties</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Minimum ‘N / O / A’ Levels / Nitec / Diploma in any field</li><li>Proficient in MS Office</li><li>Able to work 2 shifts or 5.5 days office hours with occasional OT</li><li>Able to start work immediately or within short notice</li></ul><p>Interested applicants can apply by sending your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:recruitmedical@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>recruitmedical@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></a><strong></strong></p><p>OR call <strong>Natashya </strong>at <strong>67363280</strong> for more enquiries.</p><p><em>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>Natashya Tasneem Thomas | Outsourcing Team | EA License Number: 99C4599</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W</p>",
